title: melanoma_K383_LN_GEX
growth_protocol_ch1: Live cells were sort-purified using an BD FACSAria Fusion (BD Biosciences) from collagenase-digested human melanoma samples or from PBMCs isolated by Ficoll gradient.
extract_protocol_ch1: Single cells were lysed in droplets using the 10X Chromium instrument.
data_processing: Cell Ranger analysis pipelines (version 3.0.2, 10X Genomics) were used to process the generated sequencing data.
